  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "プレイヤーは白（または黒）のスパイとなり、4つの異なる場所に向かい、CD、パスポート、鍵、現金の合計（これらを収納するブリーフケースも含む）を集めるミッションに挑みます。しかし、他のスパイも同じミッションを遂行しています。プレイヤーは彼を排除し、彼よりも先にアイテムを集めなければなりません！",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Players take on the role of a spy in white (or black), and go on a mission to go to four different locations and collect 4 items: a CD, passport, key and a sum of cash (and a brief-case to contain these things). But there's a snatch, another spy is also on the same mission. Players have to sweep him out of their way and collect the items before he does!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
